# Project 2: Sunrise Over Mountains – SVG Animation

## 🌄 Overview

An animated SVG scene featuring a sunrise over mountain ranges with drifting clouds and swaying trees. Built with pure HTML/CSS/SVG – no JavaScript or external libraries required.

## 🎬 Animation Features

| Element | Animation | Duration | Effect |
|---------|-----------|----------|--------|
| ☀️ **Sun** | `sunRise` – translateY + opacity | 8s | Sun rises from bottom to top |
| 🌌 **Sky** | `skyAnimation` – stop-color changes | 10s | Night → dawn → morning sky |
| ⛰️ **Mountains** | `mountainColorChange` – fill colour | 10s | Dark → green/earthy tones |
| 🌳 **Trees** | `treeSway` – rotate | 3.5–5s | Gentle swaying motion |
| ☁️ **Clouds** | `cloudMove1/2/3` – translateX | 30–40s | Drifting across the sky |

## 📁 Complete Code

Save this as `svg-animation.html` and open in any modern browser:

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sunrise Over Mountains - SVG Animation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background-color: #f0f8ff;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        .scene-container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 800px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        @keyframes skyAnimation {
            0% { stop-color: #0a0a2a; }
            25% { stop-color: #1a1a4a; }
            50% { stop-color: #4b6cb7; }
            75% { stop-color: #6dd5ed; }
            100% { stop-color: #a1c4fd; }
        }

        @keyframes sunRise {
            0% { transform: translateY(300px); opacity: 0.5; }
            100% { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
        }

        @keyframes cloudMove1 {
            0% { transform: translateX(-100px); }
            100% { transform: translateX(800px); }
        }

        @keyframes cloudMove2 {
            0% { transform: translateX(800px); }
            100% { transform: translateX(-100px); }
        }

        @keyframes cloudMove3 {
            0% { transform: translateX(-150px); }
            100% { transform: translateX(850px); }
        }

        @keyframes mountainColorChange {
            0% { fill: #1a1a1a; }
            100% { fill: #3a5f0b; }
        }

        @keyframes treeSway {
            0%, 100% { transform: rotate(-2deg); }
            50% { transform: rotate(2deg); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="scene-container">
        <h1>Sunrise Over Mountains</h1>
        
        <svg width="100%" height="500px" viewBox="0 0 800 500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <defs>
                <linearGradient id="skyGradient" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="0%" y2="100%">
                    <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#0a0a2a">
                        <animate attributeName="stop-color" values="#0a0a2a; #1a1a4a; #4b6cb7; #6dd5ed; #a1c4fd" dur="10s" fill="freeze" />
                    </stop>
                    <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#0a0a2a">
                        <animate attributeName="stop-color" values="#0a0a2a; #1a1a4a; #4b6cb7; #6dd5ed; #a1c4fd" dur="10s" fill="freeze" />
                    </stop>
                </linearGradient>
                
                <radialGradient id="sunGradient" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%" fx="50%" fy="50%">
                    <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#ffde00" />
                    <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#ff7e00" />
                </radialGradient>
                
                <g id="cloud">
                    <ellipse cx="25" cy="15" rx="15" ry="10" fill="white" />
                    <ellipse cx="40" cy="15" rx="15" ry="10" fill="white" />
                    <ellipse cx="55" cy="15" rx="15" ry="10" fill="white" />
                    <ellipse cx="40" cy="5" rx="15" ry="10" fill="white" />
                </g>
            </defs>
            
            <rect width="800" height="500" fill="url(#skyGradient)" />
            
            <circle cx="400" cy="300" r="60" fill="url(#sunGradient)" opacity="0.5" style="animation: sunRise 8s ease-out forwards;">
                <title>Rising Sun</title>
            </circle>
            
            <path d="M0,500 L100,300 L250,450 L400,200 L550,400 L700,250 L800,500 Z" fill="#1a1a1a" style="animation: mountainColorChange 10s ease-out forwards;">
                <title>Mountain Range</title>
            </path>
            
            <g transform="translate(150, 400)" style="animation: treeSway 4s ease-in-out infinite;">
                <rect x="0" y="0" width="10" height="50" fill="#5e2c04" />
                <polygon points="0,-30 25,20 -25,20" fill="#0a5c36" />
                <polygon points="0,-60 25,-10 -25,-10" fill="#0a5c36" />
            </g>
            
            <g transform="translate(300, 380)" style="animation: treeSway 5s ease-in-out infinite 1s;">
                <rect x="0" y="0" width="10" height="70" fill="#5e2c04" />
                <polygon points="0,-30 30,20 -30,20" fill="#0a5c36" />
                <polygon points="0,-60 30,-10 -30,-10" fill="#0a5c36" />
                <polygon points="0,-90 30,-40 -30,-40" fill="#0a5c36" />
            </g>
            
            <g transform="translate(500, 420)" style="animation: treeSway 3.5s ease-in-out infinite 0.5s;">
                <rect x="0" y="0" width="8" height="50" fill="#5e2c04" />
                <polygon points="0,-25 20,15 -20,15" fill="#0a5c36" />
                <polygon points="0,-50 20,-10 -20,-10" fill="#0a5c36" />
            </g>
            
            <use href="#cloud" x="0" y="50" style="animation: cloudMove1 30s linear infinite;" opacity="0.8" />
            <use href="#cloud" x="0" y="100" style="animation: cloudMove2 40s linear infinite;" opacity="0.7" />
            <use href="#cloud" x="0" y="150" style="animation: cloudMove3 35s linear infinite;" opacity="0.6" />
            
            <rect x="0" y="480" width="800" height="20" fill="#2a5c0b" />
            
            <desc>An animated scene of sunrise over mountains with moving clouds and swaying trees</desc>
        </svg>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
